# Build artefacts produced by `make zoneinfo` / `make verify-sig`.
# The pinned source (tzdata2026a.tar.gz, SHA512SUMS, .asc, eggert
# .pgp.key) is tracked; the extracted IANA source tree, the compiled
# zoneinfo directory, and the ephemeral GPG verification keyring are
# not — all are reproducible from the tarball.
src/
zoneinfo/
.verify.gpg
.verify.gpg~
